{"tid":771364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現瓦斯外洩抽根菸「壓驚」…支那男住家爆炸","createTime":"2018-08-08T01:44:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T08:46:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5d8563ae88e9e3710885e3e8fe682627ebf08981","tid":771364,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:44:43.000Z","msg":"這到底是喜劇還是悲劇呢？中國一名男子發現家裡瓦斯外洩，他<br />\n將瓦斯關閉後，決定抽根菸壓壓驚，結果引發爆炸，幸虧無生命危險。<br />\n <br />\n《搜狐》報導，中國山西陽泉市一名王姓男子，於本月2日發現自己家中瓦斯外洩，他趕<br />\n忙關閉瓦斯閥門，然後不知為何打開冷氣，接著他做出最誇張的舉動，竟然點菸抽了起來<br />\n，隨即引發爆炸。王男燒傷送醫，幸無大礙。<br />\n <br />\n使用瓦斯需要留意安全，並定期檢查管線，若長時間使用則要注重通風，發現有異味要立<br />\n即開窗，避免開關電燈、抽菸，以免引發爆炸。"},{"pid":"0e0e1f2894c393f9a4b37aa5b44c55f3ef74d7d7","tid":771364,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:47:33.000Z","msg":"Hey wong！望吓你坐住左啲咩？"},{"pid":"1cf7ca30dab58e77c286085d8282d9e5d01e0651","tid":771364,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:47:40.000Z","msg":"好彩無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5ef52ba7fd0276f47e3fd33e50171a896e7d65","tid":771364,"uid":34508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:48:58.000Z","msg":"諗起功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"accccd59db52a8df42b5cd850f8736a692135a92","tid":771364,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T01:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起功夫&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif&quot; class=&quot;hkgmoji&quot; /&gt;</blockquote><br />\n同老夫子漫畫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6334e9b14b89bd3947489498533f7ec632f17172","tid":771364,"uid":138713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-08T02:10:10.000Z","msg":"無知的可怕"},{"pid":"47fbaa5710a8c99d6